# 🏭 Machine Details Dashboard

A full-stack web application to monitor and manage machine details,
built with FastAPI (Python), HTML/CSS/JavaScript, MySQL (Railway),
and deployed on Vercel.

---

## 🎯 Full Project Flow

```
User opens Browser
       ↓
Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS) — Vercel
       ↓  sends API request
Backend (FastAPI/Python) — Vercel
       ↓  queries database
MySQL Database — Railway
       ↓  returns data
Backend sends JSON response
       ↓
Frontend displays data in table
```

---

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
machine-app/
├── backend/
│   ├── main.py          ← FastAPI app — all API routes
│   ├── database.py      ← MySQL connection
│   ├── requirements.txt ← Python packages
│   └── vercel.json      ← Vercel deployment config
├── frontend/
│   └── index.html       ← UI — HTML + CSS + JavaScript
└── README.md
```

