## 🔗 API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint              | What it does              |
|--------|-----------------------|---------------------------|
| GET    | `/`                   | Check if API is running   |
| GET    | `/machines`           | Get all machines          |
| GET    | `/machines/{id}`      | Get one machine by ID     |
| POST   | `/machines`           | Add new machine           |
| DELETE | `/machines/{id}`      | Delete machine by ID      |

